# ---- Content (Deniz-owned) ----
# Per 00_MASTER_PROMPT.md §9.6/§9.7: as of Faz 8, structural files AND
# the PDFs / processed ZIPs / reference solutions are tracked so a fresh
# clone has everything to `make start` without a separate ingest pass.
# Only the live drop-zone (`content/inbox/*.zip`) and error logs are
# kept out — they're transient.
content/inbox/*.zip
content/inbox/errors/

